após entrar na pasta do projeto e executar npm install, se der erro execute

npm install -g --unsafe-perm=true --allow-root

npm cache clean --force

rm -rf node_modules

npm cache clean --force
delete node_modules folder
delete package-lock.json file
npm install

npm link webpack

npm i -g webpack-cli


